{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "streamtune-collection-v1",
    "name": "StreamTune API",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API de StreamTune.\n\n**Cómo usar:**\n1. Importa también el archivo `StreamTune.postman_environment.json`\n2. Selecciona el environment `StreamTune - Local`\n3. Ejecuta primero `POST /auth/login` — el token se guarda automáticamente\n4. A partir de ahí todos los endpoints autenticados funcionan sin configuración extra\n\n**Variables de environment usadas:**\n- `baseUrl` → http://localhost:3000/api\n- `wsUrl`   → ws://localhost:3000\n- `accessToken` → se llena automáticamente al hacer login\n- `channelSlug` → slug del canal activo para pruebas\n- `videoId` → id del último video creado\n- `channelId` → id del último canal creado",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Register – Viewer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId',       body.user.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "  pm.test('Tiene accessToken', () => pm.expect(body.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\":    \"nuevo_viewer\",\n  \"email\":       \"viewer_nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"password\":    \"Viewer1234!\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Nuevo Viewer\",\n  \"country\":     \"MX\",\n  \"role\":        \"viewer\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","register"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Register – Creator",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId',       body.user.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\":    \"mi_canal_music\",\n  \"email\":       \"creator_nuevo@test.com\",\n  \"password\":    \"Creator1234!\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Mi Canal Music\",\n  \"country\":     \"MX\",\n  \"role\":        \"creator\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/register","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","register"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId',       body.user.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 200',       () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "  pm.test('Tiene token',      () => pm.expect(body.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "  pm.test('Role es admin',    () => pm.expect(body.user.role).to.eql('admin'));",
                  "  console.log('✅ Token guardado en environment');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\":    \"admin@streamtune.app\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin1234!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","login"]},
            "description": "Credenciales del usuario admin creado por el seed.\nEl accessToken se guarda automáticamente en el environment."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Creator (Lo-Fi Room)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId',       body.user.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\":    \"lofi@streamtune.app\",\n  \"password\": \"Creator123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","login"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login – Viewer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\":    \"viewer@streamtune.app\",\n  \"password\": \"Viewer123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","login"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('accessToken', body.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.test('Nuevo accessToken recibido', () => pm.expect(body.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","refresh"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Mi Perfil (/me)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',         () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene username',      () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().username).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('No tiene password',   () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().passwordHash).to.be.undefined);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/me","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","me"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',     () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Status ok',      () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('ok'));",
                  "pm.test('Tiempo < 200ms', () => pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/health","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["health"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "❌ Login Inválido (debe dar 401)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 401',          () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));",
                  "pm.test('Mensaje de error',     () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().error).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\":    \"noexiste@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"wrongpassword\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/auth/login","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["auth","login"]}
          }
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "📡 Channels",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "GET Todos los Canales",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',          () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene array channels', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().channels).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "if (pm.response.json().channels.length > 0) {",
                  "  const first = pm.response.json().channels[0];",
                  "  pm.environment.set('channelSlug', first.slug);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('channelId',   first.id);",
                  "  console.log('channelSlug guardado:', first.slug);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/channels?limit=20&offset=0",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["channels"],
              "query": [
                {"key":"limit","value":"20"},
                {"key":"offset","value":"0"},
                {"key":"status","value":"live","disabled":true},
                {"key":"topic","value":"Lo-Fi","disabled":true}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista todos los canales. Parámetros opcionales:\n- `status` → live | paused | offline\n- `topic`  → filtra por categoría\n- `limit`  → máximo de resultados (default 20)\n- `offset` → paginación"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Canal por Slug",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',         () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene channel',       () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().channel).to.be.an('object'));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene liveState',     () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('liveState'));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene viewers',       () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().viewers).to.be.a('number'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Canales EN VIVO",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/channels?status=live",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["channels"],
              "query": [{"key":"status","value":"live"}]
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Canales por Tema (Lo-Fi)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/channels?topic=Lo-Fi",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["channels"],
              "query": [{"key":"topic","value":"Lo-Fi"}]
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "POST Crear Canal",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('channelSlug', body.slug);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('channelId',   body.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 201',       () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "  pm.test('Slug correcto',    () => pm.expect(body.slug).to.eql('mi-canal-test'));",
                  "  console.log('Canal creado, slug guardado:', body.slug);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"slug\":        \"mi-canal-test\",\n  \"name\":        \"Mi Canal de Prueba\",\n  \"description\": \"Canal de prueba con música variada\",\n  \"descLong\":    \"Descripción larga del canal para mostrar más detalles a los visitantes.\",\n  \"icon\":        \"🎵\",\n  \"accentColor\": \"#7c5cfc\",\n  \"topics\":      [\"Lo-Fi\", \"Instrumental\"],\n  \"timezone\":    \"America/Mexico_City\",\n  \"plan\":        \"free\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels"]},
            "description": "Requiere rol `creator` o `admin`.\nEl slug debe ser único — se usa en la URL del canal.\nEjemplo: slug `mi-canal-lofi` → ws://host/ws/mi-canal-lofi"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "PATCH Actualizar Canal",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\":        \"Mi Canal Actualizado\",\n  \"description\": \"Nueva descripción del canal\",\n  \"icon\":        \"🎸\",\n  \"accentColor\": \"#c45cfc\",\n  \"topics\":      [\"Rock\", \"80s & 90s\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "PATCH Canal → EN VIVO 🔴",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',    () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Status es live',() => pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('live'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"live\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}/status","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}","status"]},
            "description": "Valores válidos: `live` | `paused` | `offline`\nCuando cambia a `live` se notifica a todos los viewers via WebSocket."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "PATCH Canal → PAUSADO ⏸",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {"mode":"raw","raw":"{\n  \"status\": \"paused\"\n}"},
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}/status","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}","status"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "PATCH Canal → OFFLINE ⚫",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {"mode":"raw","raw":"{\n  \"status\": \"offline\"\n}"},
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}/status","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}","status"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "DELETE Eliminar Canal",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 204', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}],
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/channels/{{channelSlug}}","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["channels","{{channelSlug}}"]},
            "description": "⚠️ Acción irreversible. Solo el dueño del canal o un admin pueden eliminar."
          }
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "📅 Schedules (Programación)",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "GET Programación – Lunes (0=Dom, 1=Lun)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',       () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene videos',      () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().videos).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.videos.length > 0) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('videoId', body.videos[0].id);",
                  "  console.log('videoId guardado:', body.videos[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/schedules/{{channelSlug}}/1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["schedules","{{channelSlug}}","1"]
            },
            "description": "Días de la semana:\n0 = Domingo\n1 = Lunes\n2 = Martes\n3 = Miércoles\n4 = Jueves\n5 = Viernes\n6 = Sábado"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET Programación – Hoy",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Calcula el día actual automáticamente",
                  "const dow = new Date().getDay();",
                  "pm.environment.set('todayDow', dow);",
                  "console.log('Día actual (0=Dom):', dow);"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Total duration en segundos', () => pm.expect(body.totalDuration).to.be.a('number'));",
                  "console.log('Videos hoy:', body.videos.length, '| Duración total:', body.totalDuration, 's');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/schedules/{{channelSlug}}/{{todayDow}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["schedules","{{channelSlug}}","{{todayDow}}"]
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "POST Agregar Video de YouTube",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('videoId', body.video.id);",
                  "  pm.test('Status 201',      () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "  pm.test('Video creado',    () => pm.expect(body.video.id).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "  pm.test('Tiene ytId',      () => pm.expect(body.video.ytId).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "  console.log('Video agregado, ID:', body.video.id, '| ytId:', body.video.ytId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"url\":      \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfKfPfyJRdk\",\n  \"dow\":      1,\n  \"position\": 0\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/schedules/{{channelSlug}}/add-youtube",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["schedules","{{channelSlug}}","add-youtube"]
            },
            "description": "Extrae automáticamente el videoId de cualquier formato de URL de YouTube:\n- youtube.com/watch?v=XXXX\n- youtu.be/XXXX\n- youtube.com/shorts/XXXX\n- youtube.com/embed/XXXX\n\n`dow` = día de la semana donde agregar (opcional)\n`position` = posición en la lista (opcional, default = al final)"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "POST Agregar Video – youtu.be (short URL)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"url\": \"https://youtu.be/djV11Xbc914\",\n  \"dow\": 1\n}"
            },
            "url": {"raw":"{{baseUrl}}/schedules/{{channelSlug}}/add-youtube","host":["{{baseUrl}}"],"path":["schedules","{{channelSlug}}","add-youtube"]}
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "PUT Reemplazar Programación del Día",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Asegúrate de tener videoId válidos en el environment",
                  "const vid = pm.environment.get('videoId');",
                  "if (!vid) console.warn('⚠️  videoId no está en el environment. Ejecuta primero POST add-youtube');"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Tiene videoIds', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().videoIds).to.be.an('array'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {"key":"Content-Type","value":"application/json"},
              {"key":"Authorization","value":"Bearer {{accessToken}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"videoIds\":     [\"{{videoId}}\"],\n  \"shuffle\":      false,\n  \"loop\":         true,\n  \"crossfadeSec\": 3\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/schedules/{{channelSlug}}/1",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["schedules","{{channelSlug}}","1"]
            },
            "description": "Reemplaza TODA la programación de un día.\nEl orden del array `videoIds` define el orden de reproducción.\n`shuffle: true` → orden aleatorio (determinístico por día, todos ven el mismo)\n`crossfadeSec` → segundos de crossfade entre videos (0-10)"
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "POST Copiar Programación a Toda la Semana",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200',     () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('Copied = 6',     () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().copied).to.eql(6));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
